<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Why are there regional banks? We have <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31452208.261438/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDUtMDQvbm9ib2R5LXRy=
dXN0cy10aGUtYmFua3Mtbm93P2NtcGlkPUJCRDA1MTEyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW0=
9ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDUxMSZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ2=
49bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB8a87798d" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" =
itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-dec=
oration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0=
00000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked</a> a =
<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31452208.261438/aH=
R0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDUtMDkvaXQtc=
y1uZXZlci10b28tbGF0ZS1mb3ItYmFua3MtdG8taGVkZ2U_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDUxMTIzX01PTkVZ=
U1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjM=
wNTExJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBb7f7e19d" it=
emprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"col=
or: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bo=
rder-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #=
ccc;">  lot</a> recently about the central fragility of the business model:=
 Banks take short-term deposits to fund long-term loans, and when interest =
rates go up their depositors might leave (or demand higher interest) as the=
ir loans lose value, making them fail. Giant global banks mitigate this pro=
blem by being =E2=80=9Ctoo big to fail,=E2=80=9D which means not only that =
if their depositors flee the government will bail them out, but also that t=
heir creditors might reasonably think something like =E2=80=9Cwell, if JPMo=
rgan fails, then the world has probably ended, so I=E2=80=99m not going to =
worry too much about their credit risk.=E2=80=9D<a class=3D"footnote-index"=
 href=3D"#footnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !impor=
tant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom=
-style: none !important; background-color: transparent !important; display:=
 inline-block;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a>=C2=A0But regional banks don=E2=80=99t really have that advantage<a cla=
ss=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-2" style=3D"color: #000000; text-de=
coration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #=
000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: transparent=
 !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[2]</span>
</a>: They=C2=A0are=C2=A0fragile, and their depositors notice their fragili=
ty, and they can go bust rather easily, as they have found out this year.</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">When this happens, there=C2=A0is more concentr=
ation of US banking at the too-big-to-fail banks, either because JPMorgan C=
hase &amp; Co. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/314=
52208.261438/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMj=
MtMDUtMDEvanBtb3JnYW4tZ290LWEtZGVhbC1vbi1maXJzdC1yZXB1YmxpYz9jbXBpZD1CQkQwN=
TExMjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1=
dG1fdGVybT0yMzA1MTEmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23=
cBb621e757" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank=
" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-=
width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backg=
round-color: #ccc;">  buys failed regional banks</a>, or because people <a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31452208.261438/aHR0c=
HM6Ly9saWJlcnR5c3RyZWV0ZWNvbm9taWNzLm5ld3lvcmtmZWQub3JnLzIwMjMvMDUvYmFuay1m=
dW5kaW5nLWR1cmluZy10aGUtY3VycmVudC1tb25ldGFyeS1wb2xpY3ktdGlnaHRlbmluZy1jeWN=
sZS8/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBf4a62732" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D=
"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: non=
e !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; borde=
r-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> just take their money out<=
/a> of rickety regional banks and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/31452208.261438/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2F=
ydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMjcvc21hbGwtdXMtYmFua3MtbG9zZS0xMDktYmlsbGlvbi1pbi1kZX=
Bvc2l0cy1pbi1hLXNpbmdsZS13ZWVrP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA1MTEyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZ=
WRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDUxMSZ1dG1fY2Ft=
cGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBf5e20125" itemprop=3D"Story=
Link" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; te=
xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  put it =
at safer big banks</a>.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-3" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; =
background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[3]</span>
</a>=C2=A0Some people think this is bad: Concentration is bad, too-big-to-f=
ailness is bad. Other people are not so sure. What, they ask, are regional =
banks=C2=A0<em>for</em>? Why does the US have so very many banks, so many o=
f which are small and under-supervised and liable to vanish over a weekend =
and cause a lot of trouble as they go? Why <em>shouldn=E2=80=99t</em> every=
one bank at a few big banks that are closely monitored, and robustly suppor=
ted, by the government?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The intuitive answer is that regional banks ar=
e=C2=A0regional, they are local, they have relationships and expertise spec=
ific to some part of the country. Historically this answer was often about =
deposits: You=E2=80=99d open an account at the bank in your town, because y=
ou had to go to the bank to get your money, and it was easiest to go to the=
 bank in your town. But now people bank online and get their money from nat=
ional ATM networks, and the big banks probably have better banking apps tha=
n the small ones. There is less reason to prefer having a checking account =
at your local bank.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-4" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; ba=
ckground-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[4]</span>
</a></p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But the local expertise advantage is real in=
=C2=A0banks=E2=80=99 <em>lending=C2=A0</em>business: If you want to buy a h=
ouse, a bank that knows your neighborhood will be better equipped to underw=
rite your mortgage. If you have a small business and want to=C2=A0borrow mo=
ney to expand, a local banker might have a better sense of your prospects t=
han a big bank, and might be more flexible and willing to work with you. An=
d in fact smaller banks are important players in=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31452208.261438/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhvbXN=
vbnJldXRlcnMuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Bvc3RzL2ludmVzdGlnYXRpb24tZnJhdWQtYW5kLXJpc2svcm=
VnaW9uYWwtYmFua3MtY29tbWVyY2lhbC1yZWFsLWVzdGF0ZS13b3JyaWVzLw/607f07ceef4b85=
24a319a23cB518b3f64" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">commercial real estate</a> and <a href=3D"htt=
ps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31452208.261438/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu=
cmV1dGVycy5jb20vbWFya2V0cy91cy9mZWRzLWplZmZlcnNvbi1zdGlsbC1sZWFybmluZy1pbXB=
hY3QtdGlnaHRlci1tb25ldGFyeS1wb2xpY3ktMjAyMy0wMy0yNy8/607f07ceef4b8524a319a2=
3cBbe34bb4e" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blan=
k" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom=
-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; back=
ground-color: #ccc;">   small</a><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/31452208.261438/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2Fy=
dGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDUtMTEvcmVnaW9uYWwtYmFua3MtbWlnaHQtYmUtdG9vLXNtYWxsLXRvLXR=
ocml2ZS1hbWlkLXR1cm1vaWw_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDUxMTIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT=
1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwNTExJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnb=
j1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3935f90d" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" i=
temscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-deco=
ration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00=
0000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">-business</a> le=
nding, where local knowledge is more important.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Still it is odd to think of regional banks as,=
 like, good credit-underwriting and customer-service businesses stapled to =
a wildly risky funding model. Why have the wildly risky funding model? We h=
ave also <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31452208.=
261438/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMt=
MzAvYmVkLWJhdGgtYmV5b25kLWhhcy1tb3JlLXN0b2NrLXRvLXNlbGw_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDUxMTI=
zX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3=
Rlcm09MjMwNTExJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB820=
e51c3" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background=
-color: #ccc;">  talked</a> a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusines=
s.com/click/31452208.261438/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2F=
ydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDQtMjAvYmFua2luZy1nZXRzLWEtYml0LW5hcnJvd2VyP2NtcGlkPUJCRD=
