=E2=80=9D loans that the private equity group can funnel to its insurance c=
ustomers.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That is from Antoine Gara at the Financial Tim=
es; it goes on:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Gray said regional banks were still best place=
