<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A group of Republican state attorneys general =
want regulators to block BlackRock Inc. from putting pressure on power util=
ities to cut their use of fossil fuels.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The motion, filed with the Federal Energy Regu=
latory Commission by 17 attorneys general from states including Indiana and=
 Texas, questions whether the world=E2=80=99s largest asset manager should =
be allowed to buy stakes worth more than $10 million in utilities.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CMaybe BlackRock was a passive investo=
r 10 years ago, but today it=E2=80=99s an environmental activist,=E2=80=9D =
according to the motion, which was earlier reported by Fox Business.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
