: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  Laura Benitez reports</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The risk of a short-selling ban by the US gove=
rnment is giving veteran bear Marc Cohodes pause for thought before betting=
 against the country=E2=80=99s regional banks, even though he says the outl=
ook for the industry remains gloomy.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The former hedge fund boss, who now manages hi=
s own money while raising chickens on a farm in California, said deposits w=
ill continue to be pulled from US regional banks because of where Treasurie=
s are trading in relation to regional banks=E2=80=99 deposit and CD rates. =
...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThe government needs to fix the probl=
em instead of putting a band-aid over the gangrene that they created,=E2=80=
=9D Cohodes said. =E2=80=9CTrying or talking about putting a short-selling =
ban in place is sheer insanity and will make the problem worse.=E2=80=9D=C2=
=A0</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Banning short sales might have the advantage=
=C2=A0of propping up bank stocks,<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footn=
ote-8" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bo=
ttom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !i=
mportant; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;"=
>
<span>[8]</span>
</a> but it has the disadvantage of looking ad hoc and lawless and panicky.=
=C2=A0<em>Not=C2=A0</em>banning short sales, but=C2=A0<em>having banned the=
m for three weeks 15 years ago</em> and occasionally talking about a ban no=
w, has the advantage of deterring short sellers with the vague threat that =
it might happen again, but without looking like panic.</p>
